Class Summary
MappingConditions The class MappingConditions provides the methods to retrieve the conditions from OMV Mapping objects representing the conditions of a search
MappingProperties The class MappingProperties provides the methods to retrieve the properties from OMV Mapping objects representing the object of the registry
OMVConditions The class OMVConditions provides the methods to retrieve the conditions from OMV objects representing the conditions of a search
OMVProperties The class OMVProperties provides the methods to retrieve the properties from OMV objects representing the object of the registry
Oyster2Connection The class Oyster2Connection provides the API access methods to Oyster2 registry.
Oyster2Manager The class Oyster2Manager provides the initial connection to Oyster2 registry, and the means to display results
processDuplicates The class processDuplicates provides the methods to process duplicates in OMV objects representing the result of a query

ProcessMappingIndividuals The class ProcessMappingIndividuals provides the methods to create OMV Mapping objects representing the result of a query
ProcessOMVIndividuals The class ProcessOMVIndividuals provides the methods to create OMV objects representing the result of a query
ProcessPeerIndividuals The class ProcessOMVIndividuals provides the methods to create OMV Peer objects representing the result of a query
ResultAPI The class ResultAPI is the listener for distributed querys sent by the API
